{"tid":1849492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［注意］日本人瘋狂搶口罩，當地口罩價值暴升十倍","createTime":"2020-01-29T05:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T14:45:11.000Z","uid":81783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c87cbf01892180c16f3753cdb02d7b415218031c","tid":1849492,"uid":81783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:45:56.000Z","msg":"琴日當地人感染單野出現左之後，日本同香港一樣瘋狂搶口罩<br />\n<br />\n市面基本上乜野口罩都幾乎無晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以應該有一段長時間都無得再買到日本口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多日本人上網轉售口罩，就算賣貴十倍都一樣有人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就快幾盒口罩既價值仲貴過搵日本高級囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好快變手持口罩就有閪屌既日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FfahB2y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFfahB2y.png&h=4f39e76a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y0qJxAV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy0qJxAV.png&h=5f55b975&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bR8JHB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bR8JHB.png&h=1b80147d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ysLQW2C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FysLQW2C.png&h=1b60a877&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ot7Dmui.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fot7Dmui.png&h=df8e9627&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e13foHF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe13foHF.png&h=8b30e42f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d7bd1e0f32e7f76f16322d5f446a8207484a807","tid":1849492,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:46:32.000Z","msg":"日本人定中國人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d66c223f01025f77a838ff7eb16d89a3ff04de","tid":1849492,"uid":81783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d7bd1e0f32e7f76f16322d5f446a8207484a807","tid":1849492,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:46:32.000Z","msg":"日本人定中國人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:50:36.000Z","msg":"日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ntwitter勁多日本人抱怨買唔到口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲嚴重過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7c68bdd8a5d245228c172ebc6df6fc04836762","tid":1849492,"uid":189150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:50:49.000Z","msg":"住日本既中國人係咁掃<br />\n睇fb d 日本人都有講"},{"pid":"304031f919924e552c2121085897274d297b04be","tid":1849492,"uid":1241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:52:23.000Z","msg":"日本人其實乜撚都炒你睇Yahoo 班冚家剷就知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7a251ab3a0a51f0e0090693dd7c3d516ed91d7","tid":1849492,"uid":22590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:52:41.000Z","msg":"網上搶姐 藥房大把<br />\n岩岩先買完 點會無得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa270d106bc6166e2b543d3d9b1e595c52df8c2d","tid